{"tid":786080,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無覺得世上有creator","createTime":"2018-08-19T16:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T07:15:31.000Z","uid":199211,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"22c732c5c5e8e5608cba7e4cdeda5f291039e8ce","tid":786080,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:41:17.000Z","msg":"我覺得宇宙萬物 不論係物理定律 化學 乃至生物既出現 都好神奇 無人創造嚟一切實在講唔過去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過唔係耶撚嗰種救世人既神 我講既creator 只係負責創造宇宙 世界發展成點就唔會理<br />\n好比GTA 既世界係由it 佬去設計 隻game 唔會無啦啦喺石頭爆出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而你喺los santo 殺幾多人都好 班it 佬都唔會出手 因為wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efb94c6dc5cbabac9779e7bb6252fceb6d71f38","tid":786080,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:42:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5babca01034dfa13f76f6172a1bfd7781745c920","tid":786080,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae3d63ab6ef8daeecf0432350c002794f8176bd","tid":786080,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4eb61db74223e5473e9c0615443f89022bcbbe","tid":786080,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco