既存在都不可思議<br />\n第一因之前又有第一因, 比如問, 大爆炸之前係點？<br />\n所以宇宙存在, 而非一無所有, 係一件神奇既事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"893aa161062042195b770d10e5b4b18f45815013","tid":786080,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:03:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=ouReaSsQbU8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DouReaSsQbU8&d=Na5T5XaPBVFKHouct36x3NtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=bb51b0c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=ouReaSsQbU8</a><br />\n<br />\n《宇宙論證─神是存在的嗎？》<br />\n<br />\nKalam cosmological argument<br />\n<br />\n1: Whatever begins to exist has a cause.<br />\n<br />\n2: The universe began to exist.<br />\n<br />\n3: Therefore, the universe has a cause.<br />\n<br />\n4: If the universe has a cause; its cause must be uncaused(自存的), beginningless(無起始), changeless(不變), immaterial(非物質), timeless(無時間性), spaceless(無限) and enormously powerful(全能).<br />\n<br />\n5: God"}]}